ZH: 我们需要进行一次市场调研来了解消费者的需求。
EN: We need to conduct a market research to understand the needs of consumers.

ZH: 调研结果显示，大多数顾客对产品质量非常关注。
EN: The research results show that most customers are very concerned about the quality of the product.

ZH: 我们将派人去调研竞争对手的价格策略。
EN: We will send someone to research the pricing strategies of our competitors.

ZH: 在调研中，我们发现了一些有价值的市场洞察。
EN: In the research, we discovered some valuable market insights.

ZH: 他们已经进行了一次用户群体调研来确定新产品的功能。
EN: They have conducted a user group survey to determine the features of the new product.

ZH: 你需要做一些市场调研来确定你的产品定价。
EN: You need to do some market research to determine the pricing of your product.

ZH: 调研显示，这个市场正在迅速增长。
EN: Research shows that this market is growing rapidly.

ZH: 我们需要进行一些客户满意度调研来改进我们的服务。
EN: We need to conduct some customer satisfaction surveys to improve our service.

ZH: 这次调研将帮助我们了解客户的购买意向。
EN: This survey will help us understand the buying intentions of customers.

ZH: 调研结果表明，价格是消费者购买决策的主要因素之一。
EN: The research results show that price is one of the main factors in consumer purchasing decisions.

ZH: 我们需要调研不同地区的市场需求。
EN: We need to research the market demand in different regions.

ZH: 调研显示，大多数客户对品牌的认知度较低。
EN: Research shows that most customers have low brand awareness.

ZH: 我们已经着手进行了一次社会调研，以了解人们的生活方式。
EN: We have started a social survey to understand people's lifestyles.

ZH: 请帮我们进行一次需求调研，以确定新产品的特性。
EN: Please help us conduct a needs survey to determine the features of the new product.

ZH: 这次调研将明确我们的目标客户群。
EN: This survey will clarify our target customer group.

ZH: 调研结果表明，消费者对环保产品有很高的兴趣。
EN: The research results show that consumers have a high interest in environmentally friendly products.

ZH: 我们需要进行一次员工满意度调研，以改善工作环境。
EN: We need to conduct an employee satisfaction survey to improve the working environment.

ZH: 调研是了解市场和客户需求的重要手段。
EN: Research is an important means to understand the market and customer needs.

ZH: 你需要对竞争者的产品进行一次调研。
EN: You need to conduct a research on the products of your competitors.
